snippet.title: Shadow Dreams - Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
The flag ship of Khosouf Studio, Shadow Dreams!

Explore a world of psychological issues as the embodiment of the last thought of hope to enter a suicidal mind, a fast magic based first person shooter with a strong emphasis on dealing with emotional trauma.

Add the game to your Steam's wish list now
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1088760/Shadow_Dreams/

Visit 
www.Khosouf.com/Shadow 
for more info

To be launched on:
Xbox
PlayStation
PC
